author: Ildefonso Ortiz
title: Mexico Sees 39 Coronavirus Fatalities in Single Day
description: Mexican health officials reported 39 deaths in a single day directly related to the spread of the novel coronavirus (COVID-19). The total death climbed to 233 fatalities since the pandemic first entered the country.
